      • isOutput

        public boolean isOutput(Request request)
        Check if a role has been output. This first call to this per request will return false for a role. Subsequent calls will return true.
        Parameters:
        request - the request.
        Returns:
        true or false.

      • outputRole

        public void outputRole(Request request,
              PrintWriter writer)
        Output an role (.e.g role="main"). This will output a leading space.
        Parameters:
        request - the request.
        writer - the writer.

      • outputRoleOnce

        public void outputRoleOnce(Request request,
                  PrintWriter writer)

        Parameters:

        writer - the writer.
